headline: DTE Energy Partners with ISN® to Upscale Contractor Qualification and Enhance Risk Management Process
summary: DALLAS, December 10, 2025--ISN, the global leader in contractor and supplier information management services, announced DTE Energy, a Michigan utility company providing essential electric and natural gas services, has selected ISNetworld as its primary contractor information management platform. DTE Energy transitioned to ISN to improve contractor performance transparency, enhance consistency in compliance processes, and strengthen safety management across its operations.
